Episode 18
Meng Ge came to persuade Li Bugui to drink the Lethe Water
Shen Zhuoyue became a kid to catch Ji Bofeng

5
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:31,360
I choose Lethe Water.

6
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:35,279
How did you know the words on it?

7
00:00:36,360 --> 00:00:37,680
When you let someone draw lots again,

8
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:39,440
borrow a mask from my servants.

9
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,960
I could read it on your face.

10
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,040
Then why did you choose it?

11
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,080
You will remember nothing

12
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,760
after you drink the Lethe Water.

13
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,280
But if I don't drink it,

14
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,519
your Lady and you will be in danger.

15
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,520
That being said,

16
00:00:59,000 --> 00:00:59,640
but...

17
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,800
Why don't you give it a second thought?

18
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,280
If you drink it,

19
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,479
your memories...

20
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:10,600
You will forget everything.

21
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,800
Compared to those memories,

22
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,520
your life

23
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,080
matters more.

24
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,360
Then

25
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:25,560
you won't kill Ji Bofeng, either?

26
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,600
You know

27
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,759
the reason I have to kill Ji Bofeng?

28
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,920
I don't know

29
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,000
how he learned that trick.

30
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,600
He could transfer a kid's age

31
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,560
to someone else,

32
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,399
so the people who bought it

33
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,680
could live longer

34
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,960
and the kids whose ages were deprived of

35
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,759
would grow old immediately and die.

36
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,880
So far as I know,

37
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,120
he has used that way

38
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,839
to live for over 1,000 years

39
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,720
and collected huge wealth.

40
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,240
No wonder that old man sounded

41
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,119
like a child.

42
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:08,039
But such a thing destroys the balance of the two realms.

43
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,640
Why didn't I hear about it

44
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,200
when I was in Lingyuan?

45
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,360
That's why I guess

46
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,240
he has an informer in Lingyuan.

47
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:17,480
Yes.

48
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,320
And I was taken away

49
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,040
and almost killed by him

50
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,000
in my previous life.

51
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,520
My parents risked their lives to save me

52
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,280
and they

53
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,560
were killed by him.

54
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,040
Let us

55
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,880
put the Lethe Water aside.

56
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,000
I need to tell Lady Destiny about it

57
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,520
and expose it

58
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,200
to the whole world.

59
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,000
Little Gourd.

60
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,440
Yes.

61
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,399
Lady, a man named Ji Bofeng

62
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,480
in Qingchuan

63
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,359
can increase and reduce the age of people

64
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,480
and seems to have an informer in Lingyuan.

65
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,760
Please look into it.

66
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,160
I can't make Li Bugui drink the Lethe Water

67
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,799
before finding the truth.

68
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,280
Please understand it.

69
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:34,760
The letter is sent to Lethe Hall of Lingyuan.

70
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,000
