73
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,240
Haven't you lied enough?

74
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,360
You have my word.

75
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,320
From now on,

76
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,640
each word I tell you

77
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,399
will be true.

78
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,280
I will never deceive you.

79
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,280
Now we are talking.

80
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,080
Why hasn't Lingyuan

81
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,040
written in reply?

82
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,160
It's been a while.

83
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,720
Don't they need time to investigate it?

84
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,080
She isn't worried yet.

85
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,240
Why are you so anxious?

86
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,840
It's someone from Lingyuan.

87
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,760
Sister? What brings you here?

88
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,920
Yo, I'm here to see you.

89
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,080
We heard you were wounded,

90
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,760
so Lady and I got so anxious.

91
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,320
How are you doing now?

92
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,360
Don't worry. I've recovered already.

93
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,560
How is Lady?

94
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,919
And Ji Bofeng's case,

95
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,880
have you found the truth?

96
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,120
She is fine.

97
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,160
It's just Ji Bofeng's case

98
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,160
is complicated,

99
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,920
so we shall keep it a secret

100
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,920
before finding the truth.

101
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:46,679
Okay.

102
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,400
We are looking into it secretly,

103
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,440
don't worry.

104
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,120
Good then.

105
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,680
By the way,

106
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,760
there are many delicious things in Qingchuan.

107
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,640
Let me take you to try them.

108
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,159
Okay.

109
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:02,920
Meng Yo.

110
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,960
Do you take here as your home?

111
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,760
Of course, not.

112
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,400
But Li Bugui

113
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,679
is hunting Ji Bofeng now,

114
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,800
so he can't lose the memories

115
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,040
before we find the truth.

116
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,359
Are you crazy?

117
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,360
What will happen to Lady

118
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,440
when you run out of time?

119
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:26,080
Sister, I know the law of Lingyuan.

120
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,760
If the wrongdoer,

121
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,320
is willing to be executed

122
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,400
and lose her soul,

123
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,960
the others may be pardoned.

124
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,640
I can lose my soul at the worst,

125
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,560
so you and Lady will be safe.

126
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,720
You fool.

127
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,520
Even if you lose your soul,

128
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,159
will the Emperor of Lingyuan allow Li Bugui

129
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,160
not to drink the Lethe Water?

130
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,919
Maybe I can feed him a bowl of fake one,

131
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,000
it may be risky,

132
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:59,640
but His Majesty may not know it.

133
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,840
If you deceive His Majesty,

134
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,640
you will all be executed

135
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,720
once it's exposed.

136
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,840
Executed?

137
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,200
What shall I do, sister?

138
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,200
I really can't do it

139
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,239
to Li Bugui.

140
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,520
You're in love with him?

141
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,280
I'm warning you

142
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,480
that you shall never

143
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,760
trust a man.

144
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:27,800
He could give you his life

145
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,040
when he loves you

146
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,640
and he will dump you at once

147
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,880
when he changes his mind.

148
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,480
Didn't you get wounded because of him?

149
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,760
If he did love you,

150
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,760
how could he let you get hurt?

151
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:39,880
But

152
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,520
I lied to him first,

153
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,560
not...

154
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,240
I will drink it.

155
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,000
If you will lose your soul because I don't drink it,

156
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,640
I can drink it right now.

157
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,840
You are a hero indeed,

158
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,080
no wonder my sister loves you.

159
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,880
Since you agreed,

160
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,359
don't go back on your word.

161
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,080
Drink Lethe Water now

162
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,640
so my sister may return to report for duty early.

163
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:14,080
All right, I know you have words to say

164
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,719
and I can not stay here for too long,

165
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,000
I'm heading back.

166
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,680
Yo, Lady and I will wait for you.

167
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,200
Okay.

168
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,720
You have decided

169
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,719
not to kill your enemy?

170
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:44,320
As it may,

171
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,359
I don't want you to take risks for me.

172
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,280
It's settled.

173
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,560
Okay.

174
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,760
Please, Town God.

175
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,400
Let my Bao come back quickly.

176
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,600
I'm begging you.

177
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,840
Town God.

178
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:11,640
Let my son come back.

179
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,160
I can't live

180
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,760
without him.

181
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:21,400
Please.

182
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,200
Have you lost your child?

183
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:28,840
That damn villain caught my Douzi.

184
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,440
He's my only son.

185
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,839
All of our children were taken away.

186
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,520
If I know who did it,

187
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,919
I will kill him 100,

188
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,559
1,000, 10,000 times.

189
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,600
My child.

190
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,400
Did they take my Douzi away

191
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:45,920
to lock him up

192
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,760
or kill him?

193
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,720
What should I do

194
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,080
if he is dead?

195
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,120
What shall I do?

196
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,080
Please

197
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,600
tell Town God

198
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,880
to save our children.

199
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,960
I'm begging you.

200
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,760
Don't worry.

201
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,360
Trust me.

202
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,560
I'll try to help you.

203
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,720
Town God.

204
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,760
Please. Town God,

205
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,640
save our children.

206
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,480
Town God.

207
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,080
Save our children.

208
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,520
Please save our children.

209
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,600
My Douzi.

210
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,800
Li Bugui,

211
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,280
what will you do

212
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,439
after drinking it?

213
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:34,319
I have no idea.

214
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,000
Selling soup maybe.

215
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,120
You sell it in the heaven

216
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,240
and I sell it on the earth.

217
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,800
Take it as a branch of yours.

218
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,880
Why don't you become a matchmaker?

219
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,760
When I

220
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,720
untie the love thread of two people,

221
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,040
you may

222
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,719
fasten it again here.

223
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,040
Isn't it good?

224
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,479
Li Bugui,

225
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:04,680
it seems the love thread of us

226
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,360
is going to be untied.

227
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,160
I won't forget you.

228
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,360
It's Lethe Water

229
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:22,080
and it will make you forget everything.

230
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,000
Even if my mind forgets you,

231
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,160
my heart will remember you.

232
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,120
It's said

233
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,280
that once you can't have someone,

234
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:39,439
the only thing you can do is to remember that person.

235
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,160
But we

236
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,800
can't even do that.

237
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:51,719
We have a problem.

238
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:52,800
We have...

239
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,360
a problem.

240
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,840
A lot of children disappeared in the town.

241
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,920
It must be the age trade of Ji Bofeng.

242
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,760
If we miss it,

243
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,960
I don't know

244
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,120
when we can find him.

245
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,839
Say something.

246
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:14,080
You want to put a two-generation grudge aside?

247
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,760
But there's no time for Little Gourd.

248
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,000
If I can't make it back in time...

249
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:18,680
Li Bugui.

250
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,240
Don't worry about me.

251
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,320
Just catch Ji Bofeng

252
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,400
and take him to Lingyuan.

253
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:24,680
I'll be fine.

254
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,520
