255
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:28,640
Yes.

256
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:30,439
Okay.

257
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,280
I will be back in time

258
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,120
and make sure you're safe.

259
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:34,839
I'll be waiting.

260
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:36,160
Okay.

261
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:41,120
Guys, we have a problem now.

262
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,120
None of the Town Gods

263
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,960
could locate Ji Bofeng.

264
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,640
That's weird.

265
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:48,319
Seems like they were bought over.

266
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,800
Ji Bofeng

267
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,680
is no match for Shuanzi,

268
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,640
but he's cunning, discreet and good at escaping.

269
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,960
Time is not on our side,

270
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,120
we have to catch him by one strike.

271
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,480
Then we draw him out.

272
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,200
We can't do it by using a child.

273
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:06,439
It will be our sin if the child gets hurt.

274
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,920
Little Gourd.

275
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,960
Is there a way in Lingyuan

276
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,120
which can change an adult into a child?

277
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,240
You want

278
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,080
to disguise as a child to get inside?

279
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:17,840
Yes.

280
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:18,640
No.

281
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,560
If Shuanzi changes into a child,

282
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:21,680
who will kill Ji Bofeng?

283
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,480
Let me do it.

284
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,240
I'll go there.

285
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,920
It's just my documents are in Lingyuan

286
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,480
and it will take a while to get them.

287
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,319
Too late.

288
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,199
Once Ji Bofeng has transferred the ages,

289
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,360
